        "note": "tsp"
      }
    ],
    "steps_detailed": [
      "Preheat the oven to 350F.",
      "Melt the sugar in a small saucepan over medium heat, swirling (not stirring) until it turns deep amber. Immediately pour into ramekins, tilting to coat the bottom before it hardens.",
